text: Egon Stephansen (born 22 October 1934) is a Danish former sports shooter. He competed in the 300 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1934 births Category:Living people Category:Danish male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Denmark Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:People from Vejle Municipality
